Investment Options | Lyrical Asset Management





















 
            Lyrical offers multiple vehicles by which investors can invest. We manage both long only and hedged 1940 Act Mutual Funds, separately managed accounts, and UCITs funds. Each of these vehicles invests in liquid securities, is transparent to investors, and seeks to be tax efficient.            
 






