Lyrical Asset Management, LP (LAM), a registered investment advisor and an affiliate of Lyrical Partners, L.P., announced today that its U.S. Value Equity-EQ strategy was ranked the #1 performing U.S. Value Manager over the trailing five years ended December 31, 2013, by Pensions & Investments. The U.S. Value Equity-EQ portfolio management team is led by LAM’s Co-Founder and Chief Investment Officer, Andrew Wellington, and includes Co-Portfolio Manager and 15-year industry veteran, Caroline Ritter.
